# TGF (Trivial Graph Format) ground-truth for the resolver golden test.
#
# Hand-authored to match `mvn dependency:tree -DoutputType=tgf` on the
# upstream artifact restricted to compile/runtime scopes that the walker's
# default WalkOptions surfaces from a synthetic root.
#
# The walker is invoked with a synthetic root that has commons-lang3 as
# its single direct dependency.  commons-lang3:3.14.0 declares only
# test-scope deps, and the walker reports the direct dep itself at depth
# 1 with effective scope=compile (the synthetic root's implicit scope).
#
# Format: `<id> <group>:<artifact>:<version>:<scope>` for each node.
# Edges (after `#`) are informative but currently unused by the golden gate.
1 org.apache.commons:commons-lang3:3.14.0:compile
#
